<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Hawaii Tokai International College will accept high school AP course credit as transfer credit to Hawaii Tokai International College if the student meets both of the following criteria: 1) An official course description or course syllabus to be submitted for evaluation to confirm the equivalence to a course offered at HTIC. 2) The student must earn a final grade of &quot;C-&quot; or higher in the AP course and receive a minimum score of 3 (on a scale of 1-5; 5 being the top) on the AP exam.</i>
